The suspense horror/dark fantasy story is set in Tokyo, which is haunted by mysterious "ghouls" who are devouring humans. People are gripped by the fear of these ghouls whose identities are masked in mystery. An ordinary college student named Kaneki encounters Rize, a girl who is an avid reader like him, at the caf he frequents. Little does he realize that his fate will change overnight.
(Source: Anime News Network)
Senpai ga Uzai Kouhai no Hanashi

Being seen as a full-fledged business woman isnt easy for Futaba Igarashi when her senpai, Harumi, treats her like a kid. Days for her are never typical, at work or outside of it, with all the antics going on in her life. As mishaps ensue, shell find herself growing closer with her loudmouth senpai. Maybe Futaba feels more than she lets on, but one things for sure: shes still annoyed!
(Source: Funimation)

Love is always troubling. You want to have the courage to tell someone how you feel. You want to know who he likes. You want someone to listen to your worries. You want someone to give you a push. I know how you feel, and it hurts. Because I had a past I couldn't forget. And because now I have the "power" to save them.... That's why I, Io Akashi, became an angel. "I've finally found you, the angel of Kuze High." The angel touched the girl's cheek, in order to correct Yuzuki Minato's abnormal tendency to fall in love. This is a slightly mysterious coming-of-age story where memory and love play out softly.
(Source: Dengeki Bunko, translated)
